Class HoldSecurityaccountSecurity

java.lang.Object
grafioschtrader.entities.HoldBase
grafioschtrader.entities.HoldSecurityaccountSecurity
@Entity public class HoldSecurityaccountSecurity extends HoldBase
It tracks the holdings of securities, which depends accumulation and reduction transactions. This entity delivers information over the holding periods for securities.
This table is not offered via a rest API.
